      <description><![CDATA[
<h2>Notiqflow 0.2.2</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Dictation stays dictation.</strong> AI cleanup no longer answers question-shaped speech or responds to requests intended for apps such as ChatGPT and Claude. Spoken questions and instructions are now preserved as polished text.</li>
  <li><strong>Safer AI cleanup.</strong> A new faithfulness check automatically falls back to the original transcript if the local language model tries to introduce an unrelated response.</li>
</ul>
      ]]></description>
